{"tid":1343872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發生咗咁多事 哩兩日打算咩都唔發生？打算繼續忍？","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:32:38.000Z","uid":263806,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5639cd3126acfd1977a39f006ef6f3c7d72c53","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOqxPTa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOqxPTa.png&h=f81c4f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔離post整合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGAFesX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGAFesX.png&h=df8ce08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警邊連環發射催淚彈 及 布袋彈 橡膠子彈<br />\n（有示威者表示瞄頭情況再有出現）<br />\n（求影到嘅片或者相出現）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6V6X05v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6V6X05v.png&h=8d5b6b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察X黑社會嘅合作<br />\n<br />\n黑社會血洗元朗<br />\n（有指大肚婆都被打至瞓低）<br />\n（相唔放住 希望證實到大肚婆為大肚婆）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arjCgzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarjCgzO.png&h=c89d66d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gsy0eo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsy0eo8.png&h=78dcc84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/513538563/posts/10156942413123564?s=100003674379789&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F513538563%2Fposts%2F10156942413123564%3Fs%3D100003674379789%26sfns%3Dmo&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4c5f2702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/513538563/posts/10156942413123564?s=100003674379789&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n警察包庇黑社會 （車cam影到警察等黑社會走晒先去現場「執法」）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jaja.tsang/videos/10161895364855705?s=100003674379789&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjaja.tsang%2Fvideos%2F10161895364855705%3Fs%3D100003674379789%26sfns%3Dmo&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=bf2c0866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jaja.tsang/videos/10161895364855705?s=100003674379789&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n有晒時間<br />\n<br />\n警黑友好片段<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UE70YQk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUE70YQk.png&h=ce5beb43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091741260286?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10156091741260286%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=e8bd1092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091741260286?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵冷血逼市民落車唔閂門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/218238771681471/posts/1168306153341390?s=100003674379789&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F218238771681471%2Fposts%2F1168306153341390%3Fs%3D100003674379789%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=427f26c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/218238771681471/posts/1168306153341390?s=100003674379789&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n（受害者錄音）<br />\n<br />\n建制議員（何君堯）與 黑社會合作<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMy7DUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMy7DUa.png&h=1a001feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2341373355949474?s=100003674379789&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2341373355949474%3Fs%3D100003674379789%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=f1b763a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2341373355949474?s=100003674379789&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n何君堯同黑社會講：你係我嘅英雄<br />\n<br />\n警方白衫就元朗事件對記者嘅回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Yi3WHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Yi3WHB.png&h=450fc8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n7.21 <br />\n香港發生咗咁多野 政府警黑 合作無間<br />\n而元朗黑社會件事仲繼續緊<br />\n<br />\n7.22<br />\n香港會好似平日咁照常運作？<br />\n<br />\n以家政府用黑社會治港<br />\n用警察恐嚇市民<br />\n<br />\n7.22 一陣間做唔做到三罷我唔講<br />\n但係<br />\n7.23 再搞一次集會得唔得？<br />\n理撚得佢有無不反對通知書<br />\n反正6.12 有 佢都照dum催淚彈！<br />\n反正6.14 百步梯 有 佢都照拉集會人士<br />\n反正6.21 黑社會無 佢都唔撚處理當睇唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n罷唔撚係問題<br />\n但罷 可唔可以有個地方聚集<br />\n俾大家知道民憤有幾高漲 有幾撚不滿？？？<br />\n<br />\n仲有一日俾大家宣傳<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n所謂革命 必定有流血情況<br />\n但唔應該只有我哋一面倒俾人打<br />\n警察你唔敢搞 OK<br />\n黑社會拎住枝竹 我哋咁撚多人又有直遮<br />\n無唔還手嘅理由掛？<br />\n<br />\n香港人 唔好習慣俾人打都唔還手好無？<br />\n<br />\n請唔好俾時間沖淡你今日嘅怒氣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有啲公道 有一定要討回</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJhPSkP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJhPSkP.png&h=7ec808df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcX4Ges.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcX4Ges.png&h=f8ce64a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順帶一題 自己去下啲深藍page睇下班人有幾on9<br />\n三個鐘前有啲真香港人嬲到忍唔住洗佢哋版<br />\n單拖都照洗照留言<br />\n<br />\n香港人 俾人恰咗咁撚耐<br />\n唔好再有潔癖 甚至係習慣忍讓<br />\n習慣覺得自己忍下當可憐佢哋嘞好無<br />\n<br />\n無人會多謝你哋 亦都無人會可憐我哋<br />\n只有我哋自己感受到自己好撚可憐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">社會係弱肉強食嘅世界</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你唔食人 就會俾人食</span><br />\n<br />\n未瞓嘅大家 希望睇下以家現場嘅元朗直播<br />\n以家仲對抗緊嘅示威者 就香港人抗爭時應有嘅樣子<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拎出你最大嘅勇氣同怒氣對抗</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先至會有勝利嘅一日！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WE ARE HONGKONGER</span></span>"},{"pid":"23e9e3152e1ed9baa8fced914642b6431f34b110","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:45:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"a1490e0628f99bf920893bf6a98f5a28cef24e40","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f1035dc6dc5ac9fab9a33262c27beca442c5a126","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"75db8c0abaefb848948640956e5c086b68935e45","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:46:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ea22a7cc680fa40648c0aa70a363440849076ac1","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:46:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"6b65dc16ce4cbcce4099bb9669276cbbf79520d0","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:47:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"97a521d9916ba33d9fc02db9b6c6aa0aa45372da","tid":1343872,"uid":279266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba5639cd3126acfd1977a39f006ef6f3c7d72c53","tid":1343872,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:44